<bibRefCitation author="Hentz NM" box="[461,487,1613,1637]" journalOrPublisher="Trans Am Phil Soc. Philadelphia (NS)." pageId="2" pageNumber="3" pagination="458 - 463" part="3" refId="ref9839" refString="28. Hentz NM. Remarks on the use of the maxillae in coleopterous insects, with an account of two species of the family Telephoridae, and of three of the family Mordellidae, which ought to be the type of two distinct genera. Trans Am Phil Soc. Philadelphia (NS). 1830; 3, 458 - 463, pl. XV." title="Remarks on the use of the maxillae in coleopterous insects, with an account of two species of the family Telephoridae, and of three of the family Mordellidae, which ought to be the type of two distinct genera" type="journal article" year="1830">28</bibRefCitation>
